country include 2.29 million yuan in cash, thousands of tents,
more than 48,000 cotton-padded clothing items, about 40,000 food
items, and medicines.
</P>
<P>
Local people have been organized to overcome the disaster
effects during this cold season, when temperatures are around
minus 22 centigrade at night. 
