India or the bird flu in Hong Kong to happen our country," he
said.
</P>
<P>
During the two years "amazing Thailand" tourism campaign, the
Thailand government hopes to attract a total of 16 million foreign
visitor arrivals and boost foreign exchange income to 580 billion
baht (about 11 billion U.S. dollars at the current exchange rate).
